public class VariableLattice
extends Lattice
implements ptolemy.actor.util.ExplicitChangeContext
This actor implements an FIR filter with a lattice structure where the reflection coefficients are supplied at an input port. The blockSize parameter specifies the number of inputs of the filter that are processed per coefficient set provided on the newCoefficients input. If no coefficients are provided on that input port, then the default coefficients defined in the base class are used. In all other respects, the behavior of this actor is the same as that of the base class.
